The intersection of Broadway and Columbus Avenue, at Lincoln Square, north from about West 65th Street. Following the line of Columbus Avenue is the old Ninth Avenue Elevated Line and which is under demolition at this date. Broadway is to the left, in the line of the street car tracks.
